{"tid":1862913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵大埔墟站發現可疑物　列車服務需調整","createTime":"2020-02-05T01:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T01:53:45.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff7dfa30f8cf65c0c18eba9fa2d14ec70ef81223","tid":1862913,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:31:58.000Z","msg":"警方早上8時許接報，有人在港鐵大埔墟站的路軌旁，發現一個類似鞋盒的可疑物品，爆炸品處理課人員到場調查。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵說，由於大埔墟站發現可疑物品，東鐵綫服務需要調整，現時南行及北行列車都只可以用大埔墟站1號月台上落客，而紅磡至火炭站維持10分鐘一班車、火炭至上水站維持30分鐘一班車，東鐵綫整體車程需要多25至30 分鐘。"},{"pid":"837ad929dc2fb762a13a6ee74871f701739af362","tid":1862913,"uid":313514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:35:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"287883b5a5e078e83c822d1d333e41f5e070532c","tid":1862913,"uid":115205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:38:43.000Z","msg":"屌 停撚埋"},{"pid":"a2a2cdc668fb0cb96911c2dc41b53c40760190eb","tid":1862913,"uid":265829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:43:49.000Z","msg":"如果係因發現有人中毒會合理d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f762e9b5694168a78f1d2cc3e0623abca01e050","tid":1862913,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:44:48.000Z","msg":"炸狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e7bb06e5908027f5dea1a511eb81e3679906b8","tid":1862913,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:46:36.000Z","msg":"搭巴士了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062539e859967007eb38e7d600b72ec180f9853e","tid":1862913,"uid":403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T01:53:45.000Z","msg":"popo幾時一腳踢落鞋盒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}